Miami Heat Beat Philadelphia 76ers 97-89 in 1st Game of NBA Playoff Series

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-04-16T22:13:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-16/miami-heat-beat-philadelphia-76ers-97-89-in-1st-game-of-nba-playoff-series.html
The  Miami Heat  defeated the
Philadelphia 76ers 97-89 in the first game of their National
Basketball Association playoff series.  Chris Bosh  scored 25 points for the Heat at American
Airlines Arena in Miami. LeBron James had 21 points and  Dwyane
Wade  had 17 for the Heat who take a one-game lead in the best-
of-seven series in the Eastern Conference.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  